articles.title: Ukraine’s SkyUp Aircraft ‘Erupts In Flames’ During Attempted Coup In Sudan; Nearly 20 Planes Destroyed - EurAsian Times
articles.description: Maxar Technologies released satellite images on April 17 that display damaged airplanes at the Sudanese airport where the coup attempt occurred. A Boeing 737 from Ukraine’s SkyUp airline is visible among the aircraft charred at the airport. After days of tens…
